Method Detail

write

public void write(int _char)
           throws IOException

The new character is appended to last instance of SSHConnector.SSHOutputStream.InBufferLine stored in the inbounds buffer. If the last character in this instance is already was already a new line, a new instance of SSHConnector.SSHOutputStream.InBufferLine will be created and appended to the inbounds buffer.
